metadata.name: Cornered
metadata.description:
One of the nightmares is that of being chased or cornered by something.
No matter where one runs, one is always found and chased.
And the moment one is cornered, and there is nowhere to run, one wakes up.

A dream of being cornered by something.
Have you ever seen it too?

ｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰｰ
